track_notes: Park at Ponderosa (nice cafe).  You can stop at the antennas as they are in the Activation Zone.  I prefer to go on to the main summit at Sit Watkins Tower.  Gets better northern take off and gets you away from the breakthrough from the antennas.

Total time (including ops): 1hr 40m. Maximum difficulty: Swiss Alpine Club Grade T1. Uncurated GPX which may contain navigation errors, detours and hazards. Additional route information may be available at www.m1hax.uk. Track data by Richard M1HAX licensed under Creative Commons BY-NC-SA.
track_title: Cyrn-y-Brain Linear from Horseshoe Pass. Aug 2020.
